headline: A Look At UnitedHealth Group’s Valuation As Policy And Regulatory Risks Reshape Investor Expectations
summary: UnitedHealth Group (UNH) is back in the spotlight after fresh U.S. healthcare reform proposals targeting insurance brokers, new regulatory scrutiny over Medicare billing, and wide-ranging repricing moves across its health plans. See our latest analysis for UnitedHealth Group.
